{"tid":954250,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(最受歡迎男角色) 馬國明為左個豬肉獎仲要搞慶功","createTime":"2018-12-24T12:54:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T13:15:15.000Z","uid":156068,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"72c11144ce973261504f5d8a601e80c58117cba9","tid":954250,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:54:38.000Z","msg":"又要孖住陳煒攞錢出黎搞慶功<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nnm69eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnnm69eb.jpg&h=80139ef9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vVBSkkS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvVBSkkS.jpg&h=ffe02216&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2JVjKNy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2JVjKNy.jpg&h=3afc5c65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0AbyPed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0AbyPed.jpg&h=2434ca41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無綫藝員馬國明與陳煒分別憑劇集《宮心計2深宮計》奪得台慶「最受歡迎電視男、女角色」獎項，晚上在灣仔筵開十多席慶功，出席的劇中演員包括黃心穎、謝雪芯、康華、麥玲玲等。<br />\n<br />\n請慶功唔夠誠意<br />\n<br />\n馬國明受訪表示：「聽陳煒話請慶功，我就話不如兩份，後來知道佢因為係代言人所以酒席有優惠，自覺咁樣夾份唔夠誠意，所以今晚會攞現金出嚟抽獎。睇氣氛，準備咗五位數，我老婆本都攞埋出嚟，要再儲過，所以冇得好似蕭正楠咁早結婚，希望大家都玩得開心。」<br />\n<br />\n諗住只提名男配<br />\n<br />\n問到多年來也未能奪視帝失望嗎？馬國明說：「唔會失望，因為都冇諗過自己有獎，其實最初諗住只係提名男配角。所以突然攞獎都嚇一嚇，再畀蕭正楠嚇一嚇，搞到我成個人呆晒，都唔知講乜好。」他又指對獎項隨緣，認為要天時、地利、人和配合。<br />\n<br />\n網民笑似中魔咒<br />\n<br />\n由於馬國明早年奪「最受歡迎電視男角色」時揚言不介意繼續攞該獎，被網民笑稱他中了魔咒，馬國明笑說：「我都唔記得講過，其實無論有冇獎都應該參與，冇獎就戥人開心，做人先至公道。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181221/bkn-20181221213542755-1221_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181221%2Fbkn-20181221213542755-1221_00862_001.html&d=jj2gdENwcyF8UVQX%2BVtGpG6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=94022f85\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181221/bkn-20181221213542755-1221_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"4847ae8077cf03c0b6ebed6a9931efbafa36ebf9","tid":954250,"uid":7206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T12:58:02.000Z","msg":"再老啲可以做阿叔、阿爸角色，轉做綠葉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec450f3b3fe6a8d14699da7400fc11554f5cfa6c","tid":954250,"uid":181697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T13:03:37.000Z","msg":"塊面好油<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"737b37bdbb40f369a2f426dda42c4006c69ddc3c","tid":954250,"uid":156068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T13:15:15.000Z","msg":"呢排咁多搞作似係補獲"}]}